data.description: Master on Main! Recently Renovated Ranch in Austell with highly sought after privacy. New Paint and Flooring throughout! Beautiful Open Concept living room that connects through sliding glass doors to an eye catching patio/porch. New Granite countertops with a range built right into your kitchen island! Kitchen has its own personal exterior porch with glass doors. You won't find anything with this level of privacy and sunlight in this open concept home!
